<br>
<h1> New Post </h1>

<div class="row" id="spacer">
	<div class="col-md-4">
		<h3> Posting Guidlines </h3>
		<ul>
			<li> Carefully check grammar and spelling.</li>
			<li> Ensure all information is accurate.</li>
			<li> Reference our store page when possible. </li>
			<li> Be interesting.</li>
			<li> Post something useful for our members. </li>
			<li> Use Markdown to style your Posts. <a href="https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/basics">Reference guide</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-8">	
		<%= form_for [@topic, @post] do |f| %>
			<div class="form-group">
				<%= f.label :title %>
				<%= f.text_field :title, class: 'form-control', placeholder: "Enter post title" %>
			</div>
			<div class="form-group">		
				<%= f.label :body %>
				<%= f.text_area :body, class: 'form-control', placeholder: "Enter post text" %>
			</div>
			<div class="form-group">			
				<%= f.submit "Save", class: 'btn btn-success' %>
			</div>
		<% end %>
	</div>
	
</div>	
